Package Model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Ball
    Class for balls - object that bounces off the racket and destroy bricks.
    Brick
    Class for object to shoot at with the ball.
    EditorModel
    Class for all activities related to level editor.
    GameFactory
    Class, where all of objects are made.
    GameObject
    Main class of the game.
    Model
    Main class in Model package.
    MovableObject
    Class for gameObjects that can move, e.g. balls, bullets.
    Player
    Class that represent player.
    PlayerData
    Class for ResultsModel use.
    Racket
    Class for racket - the object that is used to bounce the ball.
    ResultsModel
    Class for all activities related to result managment.
    StillObject
    Class for every obejct at the game, that can't move - e.g. bricks, walls.
    UnmovableBrick
    Class for Bricks that can't be destroyed.
    Wall
    Class for Wall -object that surround game board on the sides and on the top, preventing ball from leaving game area.
